			track your typing speed, and compete for a spot on the leaderboard.
		</p>

        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="/type" class="btn btn-primary">Start Typing!</a>
            <a href="/leaderboard" class="btn btn-secondary">View Leaderboard</a>
            <a href="/scoreSearch" class="btn btn-primary">Username LookUp!</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Powered by Bacon Ipsum API
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

